== Gold Edition ==
[[Image:Ultimate alliance gold.jpg|thumb|125px|right|The Gold Edition Cover.]]

There is an editon of ''Marvel Ultimate Alliance'' called ''Marvel: Ultimate Alliance: Gold Edition'' that has all 8 downloadable heroes and villains for the Xbox 360: Cyclops, Dr. Doom, Hawkeye, Hulk, Magneto, Nightcrawler, Sabretooth and Venom. It is currently available in the U.S. and Canada. It is currently unknown if it will be released in other areas of the world, such as Europe and Asia.

